api_list.name: Obtener NSS
api_list.description: Servicio para obtener el número de seguridad social a partir del CURP.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://imss1.p.rapidapi.com/imss/obtener_nss"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "imss1.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
